root.server.managers

Class ServerMessageManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • root.server.managers.ServerMessageManager

  • public class ServerMessageManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The ServerMessageManager is a singleton class that is responsible for handling with messages sent to the server from the client

    Omer Haimovich
